  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mateo ima 25 godina, a Luna ima 28 godina.</p>\n<p>Koristite odgovarajuću kombinaciju <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinti</span> i brojeve rečima za popunjavanje praznina.</p>\n<p>Za referencu:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Španska reč</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">uno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tres</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">cuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">seis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">siete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">nueve</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Ispravan odgovor je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintiocho</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinticinco</span>.</p>\n<p>Na španskom, brojevi od 21 do 29 pišu se kao jedna reč. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Luna tiene veintiocho años</span> - Luna ima 28 godina.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mateo tiene veinticinco años</span> - Mateo ima 25 godina.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
